      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document specifies a method to find which Registration Data Access Protocol (RDAP) server is authoritative to answer queries for a requested scope, such as domain names, IP addresses, or Autonomous System numbers.  This document obsoletes RFC 7484.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
